<title>HONG KONG: Peregrine ups call warrants on HKR Int'l.</title>
<headline>Peregrine ups call warrants on HKR Int'l.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-02-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Peregrine Derivatives Ltd said on Thursday it has issued a further 130 million American-style call warrants on shares of HKR International Ltd, bringing the total issue size to 380 million warrants.</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE	HK$9.38	PREMIUM	   11.9 PCT</p>
